  "sample_notes": [
    "ROOT CAUSE FOUND: decrypt.sh had two decryption backends (openssl + gpg) running sequentially with no conditional logic. OpenSSL decrypted correctly, then GPG failed and appended DECRYPT_ERROR to stdout. Combined output = '0x488b04d...DECRYPT_ERROR' written to .env. Fix: rewrite decrypt.sh with exclusive if/elif/else backend selection. Prevention: credential write must verify key parses as valid hex before storing."
